     Kanopy is a video streaming solution offering access to more than 30,000 documentaries, movies, and educational videos from thousands of
        producers including the Criterion Collection, PBS, Great Courses, Kino Lorber, and more.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">
     EWU Library is getting access to Kanopy through Open Society University Network (OSUN). Our faculty members are welcome to start using
        Kanopy.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">
