      </a>
      and then click on
      <strong>
       VISIT THE OSUN COLLECTIONS
      </strong>
     </li>
     <li>
      Click on Login into OSUN. It will be promoted to authentic via the OSUN sign in page.
     </li>
     <li>
      Type your EWU provided G Suite email address
     </li>
     <li>
      After authenticated, faculty can browse or search for films.
     </li>
     <li>
      If you would like to request a film, you simply need to fill out the request form on the page of the selected video.
